{"tid":2207450,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"求router推薦","createTime":"2020-09-18T07:24:27.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-18T11:58:55.000Z","uid":129393,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"5457665626663ddf6481e4b7dae972fb296e23ef","tid":2207450,"uid":129393,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-18T07:24:27.000Z","msg":"就咁一部放喺廳畀全屋用（唔打算配其他配件例如homeplug），<br />\n屋企唔大(400呎)但穿透力要夠，最偏遠嘅位隔兩道牆<br />\n<br />\n上網係光纖1000MB速度<br />\n<br />\n屋企device唔知算唔算多：laptop * 2, phone * 2, switch, PS5（想買）, chromecast, smart TV，一般同時會連大約5-6部device咁<br />\n<br />\n同埋想可以喺個router度裝到VPN，所有經router嘅device都會用個VPN（或者上某啲網時會經個VPN）<br />\n<br />\n唔係好識有咩其他specs要考慮..."},{"pid":"8a1ca4933485fbccfd48d9319b081d36c955c3c3","tid":2207450,"uid":78016,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-18T07:25:37.000Z","msg":"你幾錢budget"},{"pid":"b78d63e3e3f7634c811bab70d3ad18273efde743","tid":2207450,"uid":129393,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8a1ca4933485fbccfd48d9319b081d36c955c3c3","tid":2207450,"uid":78016,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-18T07:25:37.000Z","msg":"你幾錢budget"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-18T07:26:12.000Z","msg":"1000以內"},{"pid":"7e678c0f9b3ac7fe3a2a694c2f116e71f3911e3c","tid":2207450,"uid":50469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-18T07:27:49.000Z","msg":"Velop"},{"pid":"71dc3c373bd1fb0623634c674c16d6edf89ffc97","tid":2207450,"uid":54351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-18T07:29:40.000Z","msg":"Orbi 2件頭都要千4..."},{"pid":"04a986763222ae20664693cca87fb05fb404abc1","tid":2207450,"uid":129393,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"71dc3c373bd1fb0623634c674c16d6edf89ffc97","tid":2207450,"uid":54351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-18T07:29:40.000Z","msg":"Orbi 2件頭都要千4..."},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-18T07:51:31.000Z","msg":"@@ 我個要求要用到兩舊嘢來整mesh network咁高端？"},{"pid":"d6b19b95bb07685c9857b95015a